item.title: K04033

item.title: K04548
item.description: Unused boom set to fit Cat 345DL/349DL excavator, boom AR-MASS length 6.60 Mtr (21.6 FT), stick AR-HOE length 2.50 Mtr (8.2 FT), including hydraulic cylinders. item.title: Y00166
item.description: Brand new Barrier Mould. Quick release design to separate concrete product from steel mould. Key management of waste and left over readymix concrete complies with environmental waste management. Mobile designed concrete barrier mould which can be used as a temporary or stationery barrier structure. Interlock system to join each barrier mould. Forklift facility to locate moulds in position on site.

item.title: Y00167
item.description: Brand new 50 Tonne Low Level Storage Silos. High quality robust heavy duty steel design for long life and portability. All safety features to BS standards. Very low ground pressure to provide cost savings in relation to expensive foundations. Maintenance procedures are easily carried out due to silo design. Air compressor mounted on support frame of silo. Electric and pneumatic control panels mounted on silo (option generator supplied). V Trough screw to empty silo and transfer screw conveyor to feed production unit.

item.title: Y00168
item.description: Brand new Delta Super block mould. Mould specifications 0.7 m3 & 0.35 m3. Quick release design to spilt mould box. Key management of waste and leftover readymix concrete complies with environmental waste management. Mobile designed concrete block mould which can be used as a temporary or stationery wall structure. Interlock lego type design block moulds.
